      "parameters": {
        "content": "🧾 Invoice & Payment Follow-Up Workflow\n\nChecks unpaid invoices daily, calculates how overdue \neach one is, uses AI to write escalating follow-up \nemails and logs the last follow-up date automatically.\n\nNodes:\n**Step 1**\n▶ Schedule Trigger — Runs every day at 9am\n\n**Step 2**\n📊 Google Sheets — Reads all unpaid invoices\n\n**Step 3**\n⚙️ Code in JavaScript — Calculates days overdue & urgency\n\n**Step 4**\n🤖 OpenAI — Writes follow-up email based on urgency level\n\n**Step 5**\n⚙️ Code in JavaScript1 — Cleans and structures AI output\n\n**Step 6**\n📧 Gmail — Creates follow-up draft for each client\n\n**Step 7**\n⚙️ Code in JavaScript2 — Prepares sheet update data\n\n**Step 8**\n📊 Google Sheets1 — Updates Last Follow Up date",
